Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学摄像机捕捉到有物体靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示在主屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  让Exia作出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯  你对那艘船进行扫描
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被偷窥了  被偷窥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在提防我们吧  让他们去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从靠近的船释放出的  正是GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在船内确认有4台GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他们是怎么弄到太阳炉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  舱门打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米海尔  妮娜  要抓紧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所见到的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有错  不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认来自MS的光通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望在托勒密上着舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们允许着舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  解除Exia的待机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让刹那去简报室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到着舰许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前去普特利麦奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许着舰  谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne一号机Gundam Meister  约翰·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne二号机Gundam Meister  米海尔·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne三号机Gundam Meister  妮娜·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都好年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是亲兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  Exia的机师是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia的Gundam Meister  刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊  喜欢乱来的Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜欢那一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  对我妹妹做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你妹妹的不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦  你这小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想尝尝被砍的滋味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  米海尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手吧  动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见你  好想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊  你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是哈罗  哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  记忆丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  记忆丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  记忆丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  记忆丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  别待在这儿了  去房间谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙就是新的Gundam Meister…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次和你的想法一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说出来我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是帮厉害的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  难道你对刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种Gundam  都没听爸爸妈妈提起过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么会拥有Gundam呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吠陀的数据库中为什么会没有那种机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也有保守秘密的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳炉…不  GN Drive是从哪里得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  无法回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你们来这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来看被旧时代的MS整得那么惨的Meister们长啥样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的  开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不舒服  我去待机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会向吠陀汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊  如果是女人的话才不会理你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米海尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥  我感觉好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去船内转转
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能让我生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  能不能告诉我们  你们用那Gundam做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是根除战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你们一样  我们也是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说  要和我们联手？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  谁会那么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你们只会绵软地干涉  才会让我们出场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像所说的那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无可奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？不完美的改造人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  想打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  对于弟弟的无礼  我来赔罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  给我们下命令的人  是否对你们的武力干涉方法抱有疑问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们是闲置品？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续像以往那样继续作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将根据独立的判断进行干预
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对于伊奥里亚·修亨贝格的计划而言是必须的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这将根据我们今后的行动而显现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁把Gundam交给那些家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  得让吠陀验证数据
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀的终端单元…开着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是怎么进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常地～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说完了就拍屁股走人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那个叫约翰的  相当不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  什么时候拍的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘机拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么让他们离开行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本没得到对方的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不尽然哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们谈话的时候  我调查了一下那种叫Throne的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是战术预报员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用独立终端把报告书发过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不要输入吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜  Exia的驾驶员是叫刹那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙有哪点好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得可爱么  我一见钟情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次遇到了把他打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有任务了  有任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要让世界知道Celestial Being的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的重要情报  利冯兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得感谢神让我遇到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样你才捡我回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那次相遇是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我会成为Celestial Being的监视者也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对世界怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怎么样  我只是监视者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是注视世界的变化的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于完了  定期测试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真累人啊  还要兼职打工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试前暂停不就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝你还好意思说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个  考完休息这段时间干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想看的电影什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉  我要回趟西班牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要参加表哥的结婚典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  好好放松一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不许花心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不许花心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到处采访啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了吗  各个阵营的正式声明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说被重创的MS累计87台  而战死者则超过了200人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  根据当时在场的士兵的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有新的Gundam出现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是可靠情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看来Celestial Being还留了一手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那个士兵的名字和所属部队么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是池田那里传来的小道消息  大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上联系  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅没能完成接到的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还失去了三名优秀的Flag Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不配当队长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也没想到会有新型Gundam出现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且本来性能差距就大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有和Gundam性能相同的机体的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag是我军的最新锐的机体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达利尔  我们是Flag Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出风度来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  有从大气层突入的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  预测的降落点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和我的假说一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的能源发生器是利用了拓扑缺陷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就都能解释得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam之所以只有几台  以及需要200年以上的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能制造那种能源发生器的环境是木星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,120年前的载人木星探测计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个计划和Gundam的开发有牵连么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么伊奥里亚·修亨贝格的真正目的不是根除战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你知道的太多了…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测室通知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三台可能是Gundam的MS由DW9877方向朝本基地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体MS部队…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向各基地请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不明物体进入可视范围
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些Gundam…是新型号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达目标地点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜  开始锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作气歼灭敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高浓度GN粒子  传输
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…目标是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子  传输完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne Eins  GN MEGA Launcher  射击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo  厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手毫不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小喽啰们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长  有3台新型号的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的基地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授…埃夫曼教授…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微玩一下嘛  老哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一会儿就能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你们破坏  蹂躏并全灭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你见识一下  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Flag的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会被干掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…怎么可能啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德·梅森！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长  Flag…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是Fang哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩够了吗  该撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面还有任务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Meister可都是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要盲目追过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要让我丢面子丢到什么地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙袭击了美军的基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不详
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀好像也没什么消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～  尽做些让我们更招风的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Meister吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们…真的是Gundam Meister吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点哦  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我向你爸爸妈妈问好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事就别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告别之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈你也真是的  太在意别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  还是这样的沙慈好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有什么信念和理念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.44,0:23:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在战场上逝去的是人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.34,0:23:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又有谁落下了眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「恶意的矛头」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  否定Gundam
